Version 20.2.17.7 Nightly
=========================

Hotfix Changes:
MAJOR Bug Fix Related to Being Unable to add Data Directories to the Editor!
(Thanks to Alpha#9703 of Discord for Discovery)

Previous Changes:
- Further Improvements to the Installer
- Drastically Improved Scene/Data Directory Loading
- Scene Files can now be loaded without a Data Directory
- Splines can Now FINALLY be turned into actual objects in-game
- QOL Improvements to Many GUI's
- Fixed Several Random Errors and Crashes
- Reworked the EditorEntities Class to be Far More Reliable and Less Likely to Cause Duplicate Slot ID Problems!
- Upgraded the Recent Items from the INI format to the JSON format
- Removed More Uneeded Code

WARNING:
Optimizations Being Made EVERYWHERE RAPIDLY, please make sure you be EXTREMELY CAUTIOUS and MAKE BACKUPS OF EVERYTHING!
